稀疏矩阵与普通矩阵之间的互相转换：需要library(matrix)。library(Seurat）时，matrix包 已经自动加载
Mat1 <- as(Mat2, "sparseMatrix") ** 普通矩阵转化为稀疏矩阵
Mat2 <- as.matrix(Mat1) **稀疏矩阵转化为普通矩阵

dense.size <- object.size(as.matrix(pbmc@assays$RNA@data))
sparse.size <- object.size(pbmc@assays$RNA@data)
as.numeric(dense.size/sparse.size)
## [1] 5.773142

原矩阵的大小是稀疏矩阵的5.8倍

数据质控&过滤

线粒体基因以MT-开头。若细胞在裂解前状态不好，线粒体会破裂导致提取到线粒体相关RNA。因此一般会用单个细胞中线粒体基因表达的比例来表征细胞状态，若比例过高，则视为低质量细胞过滤。

VlnPlot 制作提琴图
FeatureScatter 制作散点图

pbmc[["percent.mt"]] <- PercentageFeatureSet(pbmc, pattern = "^MT-")
VlnPlot(pbmc, features = c("nFeature_RNA", "nCount_RNA", "percent.mt"), ncol = 3)

plot1 <- FeatureScatter(pbmc, feature1 = "nCount_RNA", feature2 = "percent.mt") 
plot2 <- FeatureScatter(pbmc, feature1 = "nCount_RNA", feature2 = "nFeature_RNA") 
CombinePlots(plots = list(plot1, plot2))

线粒体基因百分比高,细胞质量差

pbmc <- subset(pbmc, subset = nCount_RNA > 2000 & nCount_RNA < 20000 &  percent.mt < 20)
## 检测UMI数目大于2000且小于20000检测基因数过少,细胞质量差,过多可能是双细胞
VlnPlot(pbmc, features = c("nFeature_RNA", "nCount_RNA", "percent.mt"), ncol = 3)

具体选定的cutoff可以根据质控指标的数据分布微调

数据标准化

pbmc <- NormalizeData(pbmc, normalization.method = "LogNormalize", scale.factor = 10000)

LogNormalize: Feature counts for each cell are divided by the total counts for that cell and multiplied by the scale.factor. This is then natural-log transformed using log1p.

? NormalizeData

S3 method for default

NormalizeData(object, normalization.method = “LogNormalize”, scale.factor = 10000, margin = 1, block.size = NULL, verbose = TRUE, …)

scale.factor —- 将每个细胞的UMI数目normalize 到与scale.factor一样的水平

消除量纲

不同的基因，其本底表达量不同，在数据分布上，数值越高的集合，其标准差也会偏大。因此需要将各个基因的表达水平标准化到一个刻度上。也就是统计学上熟知的Z-score

all.genes <- rownames(pbmc)
pbmc <- ScaleData(pbmc, features = all.genes)
## Centering and scaling data matrix

差异表达基因

每个cluster，计算它相对于其他cluster的差异表达基因

#只输出上调结果最低表达百分比  Log(Fold change)的cut off
pbmc.markers <- FindAllMarkers(pbmc, only.pos = TRUE, min.pct = 0.5, logfc.threshold = 1, verbose = F)

单独计算cluster1相对于其他cluster的差异表达基因

cluster1.markers <- FindMarkers(pbmc, ident.1 = 1, min.pct = 0.5, logfc.threshold = 1)

单独计算cluster5相对于cluster3的差异表达基因

cluster5vs3.markers <- FindMarkers(pbmc, ident.1 = 5, ident.2 = 3, min.pct = 0.5, logfc.threshold = 1)

画每个cluster中top10差异基因的热图

top10 <- pbmc.markers %>% group_by(cluster) %>% top_n(n = 10, wt = avg_logFC)
DoHeatmap(pbmc, features = top10$gene) + NoLegend()
